{"tid":979701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊蒲吧變隻揪 妹夫打暈大舅","createTime":"2019-01-13T02:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T02:21:39.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41a547c93ff8e6ea94bbab9fd43bcf0e9d3ac41c","tid":979701,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190113/large/1547323926_4479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F1547323926_4479.jpg&h=1d686cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190113/large/1547323916_3fce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F1547323916_3fce.jpg&h=d8e4fc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴山林道4號恆貿商業中心一間樓上吧，凌晨3時，一名姓葉40歲男子，偕同35歲胞妹及姓洪38歲妹夫消遣，其間葉與洪疑飲醉酒，並因身體碰撞問題爭執，兩人以酒杯互相襲擊，葉頭傷一度昏迷，洪則臉部受傷。葉妹協助報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，案件列在公眾地方打架，拘捕涉案兩名男子，交由油尖警區反三合會行動組第三隊跟進。葉昏迷被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，其後回復清醒。洪拒絕送院。"},{"pid":"86ef7fd0586495e7150bc2d09ee26b26ab03a4de","tid":979701,"uid":22028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:09:36.000Z","msg":"加埋都成百歲人"},{"pid":"5de114d85fbc1e5ebd3e35a3dd99ebbc46739071","tid":979701,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"飲醉呢料，証明一早想打對方好耐"}]}